subject: Basketball
College Athletics
Basketball (College)
National Invitation Tournament
lead_paragraph: Rodney Williams and Andre Hollins each scored 24 points to help visiting Minnesota advance to the semifinals of the N.I.T. on Wednesday with a 78-72 win over Middle Tennessee.
